trans-unit.source: An abstract class used as a base class for other formatters, (for example, <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Syndication.AtomPub10CategoriesDocumentFormatter" />).
trans-unit.target: 다른 포맷터(예: <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Syndication.AtomPub10CategoriesDocumentFormatter" />)의 기본 클래스로 사용되는 추상 클래스입니다.

trans-unit.source: This class is abstract and cannot be instantiated directly.
trans-unit.target: 이 클래스는 추상 클래스이므로 직접 인스턴스화할 수 없습니다.

trans-unit.source: Creates a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Syndication.CategoriesDocumentFormatter" /> class.
Creates a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Syndication.CategoriesDocumentFormatter" /> class.
The <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Syndication.CategoriesDocument" /> to serialize.

Creates a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Syndication.CategoriesDocumentFormatter" /> class with the specified <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Syndication.CategoriesDocument" />.
trans-unit.target: 지정된 <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Syndication.CategoriesDocumentFormatter" />를 사용하여 <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Syndication.CategoriesDocument" /> 클래스의 새 인스턴스를 만듭니다.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Xml.XmlReader" /> to read from.
Verifies whether the specified <see cref="T:System.Xml.XmlReader" /> contains a valid Atom 1.0 categories document.
trans-unit.target: 지정된 <see cref="T:System.Xml.XmlReader" />가 유효한 Atom 1.0 범주 문서를 포함하는지 여부를 확인합니다.

trans-unit.source: A value that specifies whether the <see cref="T:System.Xml.XmlReader" /> contains a valid Atom 1.0 categories document.
trans-unit.target: 지정된 <see cref="T:System.Xml.XmlReader" />가 유효한 Atom 1.0 범주 문서를 포함하는지 여부를 지정하는 값입니다.

trans-unit.source: Creates a <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Syndication.InlineCategoriesDocument" /> that can be serialized into a <<see langword="atom:categories" />> element within a service document and contains the set of categories within the element.
trans-unit.target: 서비스 문서 내의 <<see langword="atom:categories" />> 요소로 직렬화될 수 있고 요소 내에 범주 집합을 포함하는 <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Syndication.InlineCategoriesDocument" />를 만듭니다.

trans-unit.source: Returns an <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Syndication.InlineCategoriesDocument" /> that can be serialized into a <<see langword="atom:categories" />> element within a service document.
trans-unit.target: 서비스 문서 내의 <<see langword="atom:categories" />> 요소로 직렬화될 수 있는 <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Syndication.InlineCategoriesDocument" />를 반환합니다.

trans-unit.source: Creates a <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Syndication.ReferencedCategoriesDocument" /> that can be serialized into a <<see langword="atom:categories" />> element within a service document and contains a URI reference to the set of categories within the element.
trans-unit.target: 서비스 문서 내의 <<see langword="atom:categories" />> 요소로 직렬화될 수 있고 요소 내의 범주 집합에 대한 URI 참조를 포함하는 <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Syndication.ReferencedCategoriesDocument" />를 만듭니다.

trans-unit.source: Returns a <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Syndication.ReferencedCategoriesDocument" /> that can be serialized into a <<see langword="atom:categories" />> element within a service document.
trans-unit.target: 서비스 문서 내의 <<see langword="atom:categories" />> 요소로 직렬화될 수 있는 <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Syndication.ReferencedCategoriesDocument" />를 반환합니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets the categories document.
Returns the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Syndication.CategoriesDocument" /> that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Syndication.CategoriesDocumentFormatter" />.
The <see cref="T:System.Xml.XmlReader" /> to read from.
Reads an Atom 1.0 <<see langword="atom:categories" />> element from the specified <see cref="T:System.Xml.XmlReader" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: 지정된 <see cref="T:System.Xml.XmlReader" /> 인스턴스에서 Atom 1.0 <<see langword="atom:categories" />> 요소를 읽습니다.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Syndication.CategoriesDocument" /> to associate with the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Syndication.CategoriesDocumentFormatter" />.
Specifies the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Syndication.CategoriesDocument" /> to associate with the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Syndication.CategoriesDocumentFormatter" />.
Gets the syndication version used by the formatter.
The syndication version used by the formatter.
[!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/includes/indigo1-md.md)] supports Atom 1.0 and RSS 2.0 syndication versions.
trans-unit.target: [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/includes/indigo1-md.md)]는 Atom 1.0 및 RSS 2.0 배포 버전을 지원합니다.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Xml.XmlWriter" /> to write to.

Writes the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Syndication.CategoriesDocument" /> associated with the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Syndication.CategoriesDocumentFormatter" /> to the specified <see cref="T:System.Xml.XmlWriter" />.
